::The Vok::

The Vok being that was in charge of looking over earth continues its watch, noting that the Autobots still hadn't arrived. If it could, it would have sighed in annoyance.

It turns around, sending a thought out into time and space. Another Vok arrives almost instantly.

"The Ikoto aren't holding up their bet too well. I think they're being delayed," it says, the other Vok waiting for it to elaborate. "I also think that we should take this time to prepare better. We are strong on the planet right now, but we can use more strength."

The other Vok nods. "Agreed. What did you have in mind?"

A 3d picture of Dinobot materializes between the two Vok, spinning around slowly. "This one. We already have exprience with him, and he shows great potential as a warrior. I suggest we recruit him before he ends up fighting against us."

The other's thoughts obviously show that it approoved and without further delay, it turned around and departed, leaving the first Vok to begin working on recruiting another warrior to the Vok cause.
